#

Creamy Mushroom Soup

40 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodEasy

Description

A rich and creamy mushroom soup that warms the soul, perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • mushrooms: 1 lb
  • onion: 1 medium
  • garlic: 3 cloves
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • thyme: 1 teaspoon
